{"title":"赏樱诗笺","authors":["光未然"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":5,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赏樱诗笺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光未然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱之桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（献给为中日文化交流搭桥铺路的人）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉眼樱花紫玉林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两京四国彩云新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光铺就银河路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵动牛郎织女心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱之魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（赞樱花长寿）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风横雨扫紫云英，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满树繁星忽断魂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道红颜多薄命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年此日笑迎春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕　鹤　赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（祝山本安英主演的木下顺二名剧《夕鹤》上演一千回）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨沧桑二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重来执手问平安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱花时节春光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕鹤长鸣唳九天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九八五年四月东京）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}